<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id7a57f630-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1997-01-01">Jan. 1, 1997</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/104/272/s23">section 23 of Pub. L. 104–272</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s6301">section 6301 of this title</ref>.</p>
